889
00:37:35,180 --> 00:37:36,650
There have been many disasters at sea this year.

890
00:37:36,650 --> 00:37:38,500
This is the only pair in Yangzhou.

891
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:39,760
I'm gifting them to you

