00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:36,300
Mr. Luo.

950
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:39,030
Gu Jiusi’s wife ran out of the city.

951
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:40,060
Were you the one who said

952
00:40:40,060 --> 00:40:41,420
